ANetBBS Selector v1.0
---------------------
Classic BBS-style connection selector for
Telnet, SSH, and Rlogin.

Callers connect to one public entry point,
view an ANSI menu, choose a BBS, and are
relayed to the selected system.

Includes Python selector scripts, systemd
service example, SSH forwarding support,
and setup instructions.

Created by StingRay / A-Net Online
https://a-net.online
https://bbs.a-net.fyi
